{"tid":1308921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣系列] 那天我們都在發同一個夢","createTime":"2019-07-12T04:22:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T07:28:33.000Z","uid":1806,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"30395d4b40d5e4689f213de6bcfb15c73431b393","tid":1308921,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:22:44.000Z","msg":"&lt;&lt;那天我們都在發同一個夢&gt;&gt;<br />\n<br />\n那一晚朋友時「發夢」時拍到這一幕<br />\n是義士在立法會一直用力猛揮手上的電筒<br />\n向外面的戰友作出鼓勵<br />\n<br />\n義士係夢入面咁做想帶出咩信息?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夢裡情節如有雷同, 實屬巧合<br />\n大家永遠記住由六月開始義士無私精神同犧牲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴絲齊上齊落, 繼續努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/IzgKOlLN0QI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIzgKOlLN0QI&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0FpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=6422c826\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/IzgKOlLN0QI</a><br />\n<br />\n我地要<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">專注返五大訴求</span></strong>同埋<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">留意近日既社會信用評分制度</span></strong>！<br />\n<br />\n1. 撤回草案 ❌<br />\n2. 撤回暴動定義 ❌<br />\n3. 撤銷抗爭者控罪 ❌<br />\n4. 成立獨立調查委員會 ❌<br />\n5. 落實雙普選 ❌<br />\n6. 撤回推行社會信用評分制度 🆕<br />\n7. 拆除所有智慧燈柱🆕<br />\n<br />\n再大家要記住當日大家曾經講既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">兄弟爬山 各有各做 齊上齊落<br />\n不受傷 不被捕 不分化 不割席 不督灰 不撤不散</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nCredit to:<br />\nBackground Music: Music by Les Temps Modernes from Fugue<br />\n<a href=\"https://icons8.com/music\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ficons8.com%2Fmusic&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0FpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=8cc75c82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://icons8.com/music</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://icons8.com/author/les-temps-m...\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ficons8.com%2Fauthor%2Fles-temps-m...&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0FpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=2fcf8223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://icons8.com/author/les-temps-m...</a><br />\n<br />\nPictures: 反送中文宣谷Channel 文宣巴絲制作<br />\nPhoto: SOPA, Philip Fong, Bloomberg<br />\n(排名不分先後)"},{"pid":"e6dd2e6c27c40e0975adae02c58b24dc059e3d25","tid":1308921,"uid":1806,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:24:36.000Z","msg":"<strong>[文宣教育系列] 中英聯合聲明超級懶人包 Video<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1308434\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1308434</a><br />\n<br />\n【 突發】《中英聯合聲明》之戰眾籌上線！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1308609\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1308609</a></strong><br />\n<br />\n幫其他巴絲Forward link:<br />\n【任務欄】<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1306215\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1306215</a><br />\n任務眾多，請自行因應人數及背後目的考慮做邊D任 ；黃色為主線任務；紅色係Boss <br />\n7.11 - 梁烈士公眾告別禮 - <a href=\"http://t.me/leung711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fleung711&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0FpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=5377dacd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/leung711</a><br />\n7.11 - 油尖旺區議會夢遊 - <a href=\"http://t.me/ytm_dc711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fytm_dc711&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0FpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=934f61cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/ytm_dc711</a><br />\n7.12 - 6.12一周月行動 - <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hklsd/photos/a.101378395784/10156221199385785/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhklsd%2Fphotos%2Fa.101378395784%2F10156221199385785%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0FpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=1265ac59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hklsd/photos/a.101378395784/10156221199385785/?type=3&amp;theater</a><b